title: New: IYES – No Wonder
body:
Wasting no time at all, Brighton duo **IYES** are back with a new track, just a week since they shared _So Crazy_.

_No Wonder_ is yet another slice of well formed, infectious pop which is hardly a surprise as the duo have been spouting out increasingly great music over the past couple of years. Big things are surely in store for IYES.

Stream _No Wonder_ below.

Follow our [Spotify On Repeat playlist](https://open.spotify.com/user/crackintheroad/playlist/1UB6gJIZpmiO0H2zmSbg02) for a hand-picked selection of the current hottest tracks.
